MPA (Blade):
    content.index/show/category/search/
    SEO complete
    for sharing link (Google / Facebook)
    static HTML, fast loading
SPA (Vue component):
    user interaction
    comment list / bookmark / Like button (no need to refresh the webpage)
    scheduling / notify / map interaction
    backend article editor

    Vue App 掛在 app.blade.php 裡
    使用者登入後才載入 SPA 互動功能

| search engine | frontend                  | backend                                           |
| ------------- | ------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------- |
| MeiliSearch   | simple, fast, real time   | fewer                                             |
| Typesense     | fewer                     | complex search, filter, sort, priority control    |

ProjectJP/
├── app/
│   ├── Http/
│   │   ├── Controllers/
│   │   │   ├── Web/      # Blade 專用控制器
│   │   │   └── Api/      # 提供 Vue SPA 用 API
│   ├── Models/
├── resources/
│   ├── views/            # Blade 模板 (文章、搜尋、地區介紹...)
│   │   ├── layouts/
│   │   ├── articles/
│   │   ├── categories/
│   │   └── welcome.blade.php
│   └── js/
│       ├── app.js        # Vue 入口
│       ├── components/
│       ├── pages/        # Vue Router 頁面 (SPA)
│       ├── stores/       # Pinia 狀態管理
│       └── utils/
├── routes/
│   ├── web.php           # Blade 網頁
│   ├── api.php           # Vue SPA API
│   └── spa.php           # 專門給 Vue Router fallback
